{"tid":1372927,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"或者未係時候 所以先要撤退","createTime":"2019-07-27T14:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T14:39:56.000Z","uid":162440,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"05a8df0a9c7ac4560fba113c101a77be3d36a319","tid":1372927,"uid":162440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:06:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係時候主動進攻</span></span><br />\n<br />\n或者你覺得未係時候？ <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁幾時啊？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果我地有一二百個FG係前線就足够<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">主動進攻</span></span>了 <br />\n<br />\n當然愈多愈好<br />\n<br />\n假如一日唔下定決心攻 咁就永遠都會有人係前線叫退叫撤 <br />\n<br />\n612到而今仲未够動機？名義？<br />\n<br />\n計我話咩都够 唔够嘅只係勇氣同裝備<br />\n<br />\n其實兩者可以話係同一樣嘢<br />\n<br />\n我諗大家最可能會驚嘅兩樣嘢<br />\n<br />\n1.子彈同煙：FG就可以解決唔講咁多<br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被捕</span></span>：如果有兩百個FG你地仲驚乜？我地反捕犬隻都得 （除非你對手足冇信心 咁我冇嘢好講 都已經一齊抗爭兩個月）<br />\n<br />\n可能你會話唔係個個够錢<br />\n但起碼我地可以傾下辦法<br />\n眾籌？<br />\n<br />\n而唔係次次出完來整句新口號就當進步<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後：<br />\n我建議前線巴打們開po講裝備<br />\n總結612到現時為止嘅經驗<br />\n邊啲有用冇用 造福新義士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要說，撤退，試著說，進攻。"},{"pid":"c6c5a1c6d6cd198e32a35adba0522f13ff1dceb5","tid":1372927,"uid":162440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:11:17.000Z","msg":"各位請見諒 少開post 可能排得柒 <br />\n<br />\n但盡量睇 麻煩大家"},{"pid":"8c52c34a457a2d6fcfdd68a5274c93771970fafc","tid":1372927,"uid":35155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:14:16.000Z","msg":"足够主動進攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44aafed5415f467c575b8e3cf1073d825ed9446","tid":1372927,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">728嘅所有人戴防具</span><br />\n[多圖]純防護裝備：頭盔、盾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372308\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372308</a>"}]}